<p><strong>Gap identification methods:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Read industry blogs and note outdated statistics</li>
<li>Check Google Scholar for recent research</li>
<li>Survey your customers about unanswered questions</li>
<li>Analyze competitor content for missing data</li>
<li>Review Reddit and forums for recurring questions</li>
</ul>
