<p><strong>Mistake 3: Choosing the wrong format.</strong> A calculator does not work for every topic. Match format to content.</p>
<p><strong>Mistake 4: Forgetting updates.</strong> Outdated assets stop earning links. Schedule refresh cycles.</p>
<p><strong>Mistake 5: No clear citation path.</strong> Make it easy to find and use your data. Hidden statistics do not get cited.</p>
